    Time Management

II. REALISER UNE INTERFACE UTILISATEUR STATIQUE ET ADAPTABLE

    IDE
    LOGICIEL DE CREATION IMAGE >> Photoshop, Gimp
    STRUCTURE FICHIERS
    CONNAISSANCES DES STANDARDS DE L'INDUSTRIE >> Nomination des fichiers, des variables, etc
    HTML CSS JS
    MEDIAQUERIES
    HOSTING >> FTTP (?)

    PATIENCE


III. DEV. UNE INTERFACE WEB DYNAMIQUE

    PHP, SQL, APACHE, MANGODB
    BDD

III. A. DESIGN FONCTIONNEL

CONSIDER PRODUCT GOAL
    CONSIDER THE CLIENT BASE
    CONSIDER WHAT THEY WILL DO WITH IT
    CONSIDER IF THE TOOL IS CLEAR AND PRACTICAL TO USE
    VALIDATION OF FORMS, INFORM THE CLIENT THAT HIS REQUEST WENT THRU
    MISTAKE HANDLING
    IS IT ENGAGING TO USERS


III. B. DESIGN GRAPHIQUE

    LOGICIEL DE CREATION IMAGE >> Photoshop, Gimp, suite ADOBE
    TYPOGRAPHIE
    CREATIVITY
    ATTENTION AU DETAIL
    COLOR THEORY
    USABILITY

IV. REALISER UNE INTERFACE UTILISATEUR

    USER ADVOCACY
    PARTICIPATORY DESIGN
    CROWD SOURCE DESIGN
    WIREFRAMING
    VISUAL COMMUNICATION

    USER OBJECTIVES
    USER FLOW
    METRICS AND ANALYTICS
    




